Package dbdiffchecker

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Column
    Column resembles a column in MySQL and contains column info.
    Database
    Database models a MYSQL database schema.
    DB_Diff_Checker_GUI
    DB_Diff_Checker_GUI is a JFrame that takes user input to decide which JFrame to open.
    DBCompare1
    DBCompare1 is a JFrame that takes user input to make a comparison between 1 devDatabase and a devDatabase snapshot or to take a devDatabase snapshot.
    DbConn
    DbConn establishes a connection with a MySQL database based on the password, username, port, host, and database provided.
    ErrorPopup
    ErrorPopup is a JFrame that shows a message about an error that occurred.
    FileConversion
    FileConversion can convert a Database object into a JSON file and vice versa.
    Index
    Index resembles an index in MySQL and contains index info.
    JFrameV2
    JFrameV2 is a JFrame that has all of the common methods that any JFrame in this package uses.
    Result
    Result is a JFrame that shows the provided data to the user.
    Schema
    Schema holds common methods and instance variables for Schema subclasses.
    StopWatch
    StopWatch models a stopwatch and can determine how much time has elapsed since the last start and end method calls.
    Table
    Table resembles a table in MySQL and contains info about the table's columns.
    Views
    Views resembles an view in MySQL and contains view info.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DatabaseDiffernceCheckerException
    Db_conn establishes a connection with a MySQL database based on the password, username, port, host, and database provided.
